item.description:
@Sleep wrote:

[quote=“exe626, post:3, topic:62315”][quote author=Mr me link=topic=89854.msg950462#msg950462 date=1172727529]
Well my friend is hitomi adrea that is a pmod i will not tell rest
[/quote]
Wow, informative…
About half the people on my list up there are mods…
Its nothing special…
They can just mute you if they feel like it, They’ve muted me before :O[/quote]

Actually, a P-Mod cannot mute unless there is grounds to do so. If a P-Mod were to go around muting everyone that asked for it a few things would happen…

  1. Loss of Crown
  2. Temp ban
  3. Maybe a temp mute if the circumstances prove enough to issue a temp mute.
